/* ---- Changelog ---- */
"changelog.title": "Changelog",
"changelog.notifications": "Notifications",
"changelog.content": "<div style=\"margin-bottom:16px\"><b>V1.0</b> — 2026.06.28<br><b>Free Chat</b><br>(1) Sidebar conversation management: create, switch, rename, delete conversations with auto-generated titles (AI summary or auto-truncation)<br>(2) Full-featured chat UI: Markdown rendering (headings, tables, code highlighting), SSE streaming, Enter to send / Shift+Enter for newline<br>(3) Deep Think mode: AI outputs step-by-step reasoning before the final answer<br>(4) Three chat personas: Standard (professional & friendly), Lively (casual & energetic), Expert (rigorous & in-depth)<br>(5) Instant KB retrieval: toggle KB in chat, AI auto-searches and injects matching references, citing sources in output<br>(6) File upload in chat: supports image/document attachments, document content auto-extracted and injected into context<br>(7) Full-text search to quickly locate historical messages<br>(8) Chat export: export full conversation in Markdown format</div><div style=\"margin-bottom:16px\"><b>V0.9</b> — 2026.06.27<br><b>Weekly Report Module</b><br>(1) Four report templates: Graduate Research Weekly, R&D Project Weekly, Tech Survey Weekly, Ops Stability Weekly<br>(2) Two styles (structured/narrative) with bilingual (Chinese/English) output — AI extracts key info from raw notes<br>(3) Single input box design — paste scattered notes, AI organizes into complete reports<br>(4) Streaming generation, copy, Word export, template extraction, todo extraction<br><b>Meeting Minutes Improvements</b><br>(5) Transcription model selection: fast mode (small, for real-time) and quality mode (medium, for batch), user-selectable</div><div style=\"margin-bottom:16px\"><b>V0.8</b> — 2026.06.26<br><b>Email Module Upgrade</b><br>(1) Reply mode: paste original email, AI analyzes context and composes appropriate reply with proper tone<br>(2) Email drafting optimization: restructured prompts for more natural workplace tone, less formulaic, extracts key points from original emails<br><b>Knowledge Base Precision</b><br>(3) Precise reference matching: reference numbers in AI output auto-linked to KB chunks, supports multiple citation formats, unquoted chunks no longer saved<br>(4) Text overlap fallback: 2-gram overlap detection finds implicitly used KB content even without explicit citations<br>(5) KB search relevance filtering: automatically skips irrelevant results to avoid noise in AI output</div><div style=\"margin-bottom:16px\"><b>V0.7</b> — 2026.06.24<br><b>Full Interface i18n</b><br>(1) New frontend i18n engine: data-i18n attributes + t() API with automatic DOM refresh on language switch<br>(2) Language switcher in Settings (Chinese / English), auto-detects browser language, persisted in localStorage<br>(3) Chinese & English packs cover login, nav, 8 modules, settings, templates, KB, history, todos, tavern, toasts, and more<br>(4) Backend detects Accept-Language header and returns error messages in the request's language</div><div style=\"margin-bottom:16px\"><b>V0.6</b> — 2026.06.22<br><b>Complete UI Overhaul</b><br>(1) Login page redesign: deep blue gradient, glassmorphism card, avatar, subtitle carousel with 20 buzzwords<br>(2) Global glassmorphism: nav bar, main card, bottom bar, settings panel, history panel — all frosted glass<br>(3) Nav bar restructured: brand fixed left, tool tabs centered, dark mode adaptive<br>(4) Micro-interactions added to all notifications, modals, buttons, inputs<br><b>The Tavern</b><br>(5) Pixel-art status log in bottom-right corner, 102 workplace \"event broadcasts\" scrolling<br>(6) Auto-popup on timer, manual trigger, drag to reposition, position memory<br>(7) Independent toggles for auto-broadcast and full hide in settings<br><b>AI Upgrade</b><br>(8) All module prompts rewritten — more natural language, better structure, less \"AI flavor\"<br>(9) PRD generation significantly longer, frontend demo more complete<br>(10) Smart todo parsing: \"Meet Zhang tomorrow 3pm\" auto-detects task, time, person<br>(11) Browser title cycles through 100 creative slogans<br><b>Security & UX</b><br>(12) Security question + password reset flow added<br>(13) Loading indicators for non-streaming ops (follow-up, todo extract, correction)<br>(14) Multiple backend stability fixes</div><div style=\"margin-bottom:16px\"><b>V0.5</b> — 2026.06.21<br>(1) API Key encryption: PBKDF2 + AES-GCM in browser, unlocked by login password, plaintext only in sessionStorage<br>(2) Todo pipeline rework: AI extraction with relative time (minute precision), batch edit review modal, regex fallback<br>(3) Todo batch operations: select all, mark done/pending, batch delete, auto-reset on refresh<br>(4) Notification badge fixed: shows correctly for empty todos, real-time sync, formatted display<br>(5) Follow-up fixes: modal replacing prompt(), SSE returns record_id, X-Api-Key passthrough, callback signature fix<br>(6) Security hardening: Markdown XSS whitelist filter, dead code cleanup<br>(7) Database refactor: singleton connection pool + lightweight migration (_db_version table), token stats fix<br>(8) Engineering: unified version.py, .gitignore sensitive files, CDN offline fallback, start/stop scripts<br>(9) KB quick-paste selector + polish module layout fixes</div><div style=\"margin-bottom:16px\"><b>V0.4</b> — 2026.06.21<br>(1) Knowledge Base: create KB, upload txt/md/docx/pdf, auto-chunk, jieba full-text search<br>(2) Auto KB retrieval during AI generation: matched materials injected, output cites source filenames<br>(3) KB reference badges: [Ref N · source] rendered as clickable blue badges<br>(4) Template instruction passthrough fixed: frontend→Pydantic→all endpoints custom_instruction pipeline<br>(5) Template edit echo-back fixed: form no longer clears, module checkboxes restored correctly<br>(6) PPT outline generation/export error fixed<br>(7) Reportese streaming \"word eating\" fixed<br>(8) KB search no results fixed<br>(9) KB upload JS error fixed<br>(10) PDF upload freeze fixed: 10MB/50 page/50k char limits + async parsing<br>(11) PRD streaming generation fixed<br>(12) Template endpoint name mapping fixed<br>(13) Template instruction injection for continue/extract-todos/correct-text<br>(14) PyPDF2 added to requirements.txt</div><div style=\"margin-bottom:16px\"><b>V0.3</b> — 2026.06.20<br>(1) New modules: Requirements Analysis, PRD (with runnable Demo HTML), PPT Outline<br>(2) Speech-to-text: whisper.cpp medium model, full transcript + real-time mode<br>(3) AI smooth correction: DeepSeek fixes recognition errors, removes duplicates, improves fluency<br>(4) Multi-language support: auto-detect Chinese, English, mixed input<br>(5) Dark mode + custom background image upload<br>(6) Safety guard: prompt injection interception, keyword filter, auto-redaction<br>(7) Recognition quality: beam search beam_size=5 + silence buffer<br>(8) Document processing: Word export, TXT/MD/DOCX extraction, full SSE streaming</div><div style=\"margin-bottom:16px\"><b>V0.2</b> — 2026.06.19<br>(1) JWT account system: register, login, change password, delete account<br>(2) Usage stats + history management<br>(3) Rate limiting + local preference storage<br>(4) Frontend refactor: Material Icons library + CSS variable design system</div><div><b>V0.1</b> — 2026.06.18<br>(1) Initial release: text summarization, email drafting, meeting minutes, report polishing, management translation<br>(2) DeepSeek API · SQLite storage · FastAPI backend · SPA frontend</div>",

